dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents parks for Brown County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Brown_Parks_2017.gdb'.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: [Brown County Planning & Land Services Dept, Brown County Public Safety & Communications, Municipalities within Brown County, and other sources.]
dataIdInfo.suppInfo:
For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://browncounty.maps.arcgis.com/apps/webappviewer/index.html?id=61fba3fd419045e48aa6ba759838387c
This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
